channel.title: 22+ EP - mstar [pop, electronica, glitch]
channel.description:
Well...I'm back. This time I have an extension/expansion for my original album 22 (about a month ago...)
This EP contains: 3 VIP mixes of songs from 22 (venom, sparkle, and hold on a bit) 2 original songs (hex and ANV6 entry lightshadow) and 2 remixes of classic Auxy stuff Pay Phone (mstar edit) - originally produced by Fantom '87 (rip) Mixed Mood (Moody Mix) -a remix of the Mixed Mood demo song
enjoy! - mstar [22+ EP SC Link](https://soundcloud.com/mstar_music/sets/22-plus_ep)
